<item>
            <title>[DERBY-2030] &apos;set schema sys&apos; followed by &apos;show tables&apos; does not show tables in sys schema</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2030</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you create a new database in IJ, followed by &apos;set schema sys&apos; and then &apos;show tables&apos;, ij shows no tables in the schema. This is because ij&apos;s show tables command only shows system tables if a schema is provided.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
